com.yahoo.documentapi.messagebus.protocol

Class AsyncInitializationPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yahoo.documentapi.messagebus.protocol.AsyncInitializationPolicy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DocumentProtocolRoutingPolicy, com.yahoo.messagebus.routing.RoutingPolicy, Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExternalSlobrokPolicy

    public abstract class AsyncInitializationPolicy
extends Object
implements DocumentProtocolRoutingPolicy, Runnable
    Abstract class for routing policies that need asynchronous initialization. This is recommended if the routing policy needs configuration, or synchronization with other sources. If this policy is not used in those cases, the messagebus thread might hang waiting for the other sources, causing messages to other routes to be blocked.
